Comment: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.78,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I couldn’t help it so I threw it all out
Comment: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:21.44,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I erased all of my emotions
Comment: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:26.06,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,But I couldn’t erase you
Comment: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:29.64,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,Because my heart was too sad
Comment: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.18,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I just need to live like this, I just need to breathe
Comment: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.80,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I just need to be alive, why can’t I?
Comment: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.26,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I said it’s okay
Comment: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:43.82,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,This is better for me
Comment: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.99,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I was afraid that I’d get cut
Comment: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:49.00,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,By your sharp, knife-like words
Comment: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.53,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I just need to breathe and eat
Comment: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.50,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,To endure through this
Comment: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:58.61,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I was a coward, I wanted to endure through
Comment: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:02.76,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I don’t want to let go of myself
Comment: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:06.13,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I don’t want to ruin myself anymore
Comment: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.93,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,Memories that aren’t ending even when it’s over
Comment: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:12.96,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,I have no confidence to win over it
Comment: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:17.16,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,Love, in the end
Comment: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:21.12,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,Is a lie to just one person
Comment: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.15,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,Now look at me forgetting you
Comment: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.88,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,With your eyes wide open
Comment: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:29.49,Trans,,0,0,0,karaoke,Don’t ever forget me
